###

### Get featured projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/featured
Content-Type: application/json

### With limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/featured?limit=6
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get project statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/stats
Content-Type: application/json

